---
const props = Astro.props;

import ImageCard from '../../ImageCard.astro';
import icon from '../../../assets/inventory/staff/Diffusing Prism.png'
---

<ImageCard image={icon} title="Diffusing Prism">
<p>Increases M.ATK by <span class="text-purple-500">5%</span>-<span class="text-purple-500">10%</span>. Upon casting AoE Attack, for each <span class="text-orange-500">1</span> target hit, increases [<span class="text-yellow-500">magical DMG</span>] and [<span class="text-yellow-500">piercing DMG</span>] dealt by <span class="text-orange-500">5</span>-<span class="text-orange-500">10%</span>, up to <span class="text-orange-500">10</span>-<span class="text-orange-500">20%</span>.</p>
</ImageCard>
